---
title: QuoteX - Qwen Cloud Commerce Autopilot Architecture
---
flowchart TB
    INPUT["Seller and buyer channels<br/>Voice | text | product photo"]
    UI["QuoteX browser application<br/>GitHub Pages | responsive TypeScript UI"]
    FC["Alibaba Cloud Function Compute<br/>Node.js API | Japan (Tokyo)<br/>Validation | auth | orchestration"]
    QWEN["Qwen Cloud intelligence<br/>Qwen3.7-Plus | Vision | ASR<br/>Voice Design | TTS | Image | HappyHorse"]
    SKILLS["Governed commerce agent<br/>6 typed skills: request | memory | catalog<br/>freight | pricing | risk policy"]
    GATE{"Human approval<br/>required"}
    OUTPUT["Review-ready business outputs<br/>Quote | campaign | voice answer<br/>Amazon | eBay | Alibaba.com drafts"]
    BLOCK["Outbound action blocked<br/>No offer or listing sends automatically"]
    MEMORY["Live judge persistence<br/>Bounded memory adapter<br/>Listings | memories | agent evidence"]
    TABLE["Production data path<br/>Alibaba Tablestore<br/>Listings | memory | run ledger"]
    OSS["Production media path<br/>Private Alibaba OSS<br/>Original and generated assets"]
    SLS["Observability path<br/>Alibaba SLS<br/>Request | model | runtime metrics"]

    INPUT --> UI
    UI -->|"HTTPS + session access token"| FC
    FC <-->|"OpenAI-compatible and DashScope APIs"| QWEN
    QWEN -->|"Plans tool calls"| SKILLS
    FC -->|"Executes trusted code"| SKILLS
    SKILLS --> GATE
    GATE -->|"Approved by a person"| OUTPUT
    GATE -->|"Pending or rejected"| BLOCK
    FC <--> MEMORY
    FC -.->|"Durable deployment"| TABLE
    FC -.->|"Encrypted media"| OSS
    FC -.->|"Structured telemetry"| SLS

